1676412007132751277.Text: These are the rules of the Fighters Guild. My duties are to my Lords and brethren. In all ways, I should proceed with honor and valor. I must keep a keen and watchful mind and never succumb to the craven tricks of the weak. It is traitorous to fight or thieve from other members of my guild. If I break these rules, I must speak with at least a Warder of the Guild to redeem my standing.
